HEADWORD: Accite
<hw>Ac*cite"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>accitus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>accire</ets>, <ets>accere</ets>, to
call for; <ets>ad</ets> + <ets>ciere</ets> to move, call. See
<er>Cite</er>.]</ety> <def>To cite; to summon.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our heralds now <qex>accited</qex> all that were⟦br⟧
Endamaged by the Elians.</q> <rj><qau>Chapman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

